<div align="center" style="height:40px; display:inline; background:white;"><img src="http://www.aim.com/remote/gr/MNB_online.gif" style="display:inline;" alt="online" title="online" border="0"/> = Online  <img src="http://www.aim.com/remote/gr/MNB_offline.gif"  style="display:inline;" alt="offline" title="offline" border="0"/> = Offline</div></td>
</center>